            <div id="cite-standard" class="tab " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-4" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_standard rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_standard rendering_contributiontojournal_standard"><a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://pure.eur.nl/en/publications/representing-and-utilizing-clinical-textual-data-for-real-world-s/" class="link"><span><strong>Representing and utilizing clinical textual data for real world studies: An OHDSI approach.</strong></span></a> / Keloth, Vipina K.; Banda, Juan M.; Gurley, Michael et al. <br />In: <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span>Journal of Biomedical Informatics</span></a>, Vol. 142, 104343, 06.2023.<p class="type"><span class="type_family">Research output<span class="type_family_sep">: </span></span><span class="type_classification_parent">Contribution to journal<span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span></span><span class="type_classification">Article</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>Academic</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>peer-review</span></p></div>
